# Crossmint Megaverse Challenge
My submission for the Crossmint Megaverse coding challenge.

## Features
- Phase 1: Automated X shape using Polyanets
- Phase 2: Full Megaverse automated from `/goal` map
- Includes retry and rate-limit handling
- Reset scripts for full grid cleanup

## How to Run
1Ô∏è Clone repo:
git clone https://github.com/DexterCooke/crossmint_challenge.git
cd crossmint_challenge

2 Setup virtualenv:
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt

3 Phase 1: 
python polyanet_cross.py

4 Phase 2: 
python phase2_create_megaverse.py

5 Reset phase 1: 
python reset_polyanets.py

6 Reset phase 2:
python reset_phase_2.py